Visually identified “elbows” were observed in WCSS plots for the FDS muscle at 15% and 35% of MVC, indicating that clustering analysis was appropriate. Silhouette scores were subsequently calculated to identify the optimal number of clusters, with the highest value for both force levels occurring when \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
